## Notes
- All implementation will preserve existing working logic unless defects exist
- Prefer modular monolith over unnecessary distributed complexity
- Local AI inference preferred with optional NVIDIA GPU acceleration
- Self-hosted first, broker/vendor independent, open-source/low-cost preferred
- No mandatory cloud/SaaS/paid dependencies
- Local deployment fully functional, offline capable where practical
- Paper mode primary, manual-first execution, live trading disabled by default
- Explicit enablement required for dangerous actions

